ZH: 我的姑妈是我爸爸的妹妹。
EN: My aunt is my father's younger sister.

ZH: 姑妈也是家里最爱煮菜的人。
EN: My aunt is also the person in our family who loves cooking the most.

ZH: 我姑妈的蛋糕真好吃！
EN: My aunt's cake is so delicious!

ZH: 姑妈总是关心我的学业和健康。
EN: My aunt always cares about my studies and health.

ZH: 我姑妈今年要去旅行，我很羡慕她。
EN: My aunt is going on a trip this year, I am very envious of her.

ZH: 姑妈的笑声总是让我感到开心。
EN: My aunt's laughter always makes me happy.

ZH: 我明天要去姑妈家拜访她。
EN: I will visit my aunt's house tomorrow.

ZH: 我的姑妈是一位优秀的医生。
EN: My aunt is an excellent doctor.

ZH: 姑妈对我说的话让我很受鼓舞。
EN: The words my aunt said to me are very inspiring.

ZH: 请姑妈帮我修理这台电脑好吗？
EN: Aunt, can you please help me repair this computer?

ZH: 我的姑妈喜欢看韩剧。
EN: My aunt enjoys watching Korean dramas.

ZH: 今年过年我们将和姑妈一起度过。
EN: We will celebrate Chinese New Year with my aunt this year.

ZH: 姑妈教我如何织毛衣。
EN: My aunt taught me how to knit a sweater.

ZH: 每年夏天，姑妈都会带我去海边度假。
EN: Every summer, my aunt takes me to the seaside for vacation.

ZH: 姑妈喜欢种花，并且她的花园非常美丽。
EN: My aunt enjoys gardening, and her garden is very beautiful.

ZH: 姑妈非常喜欢瑜伽，每天都要练习。
EN: My aunt loves yoga and practices it every day.

ZH: 姑妈对家族历史了解得非常清楚。
EN: My aunt has a clear understanding of our family's history.

ZH: 我的姑妈有两个可爱的孩子。
EN: My aunt has two lovely children.

ZH: 姑妈的手艺非常好，她会做各种美食。
EN: My aunt is very skilled and can make various delicious dishes.

ZH: 每年圣诞节，我都会收到姑妈送的礼物。
EN: Every Christmas, I receive gifts from my aunt.
